### ==============================================
### UPLOAD ENDPOINTS
### ==============================================
### Upload single file
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/file
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="photo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/photo.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload multiple files
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/files
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/photo1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload document
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/document
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="doc.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./path/to/doc.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload video
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/video
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="video.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< ./path/to/video.mp4
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Get upload status
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/status/upload-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Delete file
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/upload/file/public-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


